(13008, 'Novistoric 20mg 14 f.c. tab', 'نوفيستوريك 20مجم 14 قرص', '53', '72', 'Rosuvastatin', 'Fpi', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'خافض للدهون والكوليسترول', 'Antihyperlipidemic', '20mg', 'The FDA monograph states that rosuvastatin is indicated as an adjunct to diet in the treatment of triglyceridemia, Primary Dysbetalipoproteinemia (Type III Hyperlipoproteinemia), and Homozygous Familial Hypercholesterolemia.[F4649]
